(5, 'Software Freedom Day 2013 ', '<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/9933504375_5782a90a86_z.jpg\" style=\"height:640px; width:426px\" /></p>\n\n<p>Kelompok Studi Linux - Universitas Budi Luhur (KSL-UBL) akan mengadakan Seminar Software Freedom Day (Sabtu, 28 September 2013, 10:00 WIB). Acara Software Freedom Day ini merupakan acara tahunan KSL-UBL, untuk tahun ini acaranya bertemakan &quot;Database Security&quot; dengan pembicara Khulung Bursa (Oracle), dan Rusmanto Maryanto (InfoLinux).</p>\n', 'Software Freedom Day 2013 ', '<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/9933504375_5782a90a86_z.jpg\" style=\"height:640px; width:426px\" /></p>\n\n<p>The Linux Study Group - Budi Luhur University (KSL-UBL) will hold a Freedom Day Software Seminar (Saturday, September 28, 2013, 10:00 WIB). This Freedom Day Software program is an annual event of KSL-UBL, for this year the program has the theme &quot;Database Security&quot; with the speaker Khulung Bursa (Oracle), and Rusmanto Maryanto (InfoLinux).</p>\n', 0, 0, '2018-09-08 10:19:56', '2018-09-08 10:19:56', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, 1, 1),
(6, 'Software Freedom Day 2013 @ Universitas Budi Luhur ', '<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-1.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Pada 28 September 2013 Kelompok Studi Linux dari Universitas Budi Luhur juga berpartisipasi dalam Hari Kebebasan Perangkat Lunak mengadakan acara 2013, acara pertama adalah Seminar dengan tema diskusi mengenai pengamanan Sistem Data Base yang diberi tema &quot; Optimalisasi dan Pengamanan Database &quot;.<br />\n<br />\nAcara ini menampilkan dua pembicara, pembicara pertama oleh Rusmanto Maryanto, yang menjabat sebagai Ketua Asosiasi Sumber Indonesia Open Source materi tentang pengembangan Perangkat Lunak Open Source Gratis di Indonesia dan yang kedua oleh Bursa Khulung Speaker yang menjabat sebagai Oracle Instructor membahas tentang cara membuat database yang aman dari berbagai sisi aplikasi.<br />\n<br />\nSelain Seminar dan Acara Workshop yang diselenggarakan pada tangga 27 September 2013 yang membahas bagaimana pemasangan linux dan cara membuat server web dan untuk hiburan ada acara pertandingan game dengan nama permainan di arena open play di sistem operasi linux.<br />\n<br />\nSebelum kami mengadakan seminar<br />\nPresentasi Oleh Rusmanto Maryanto (Ketua Harian Asosiasi Open Source Indonesia)</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-2.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-3.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Presentation By Khulung Bursa (Oracle Instructure)</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-4.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-5.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Peserta seminar</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-6.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-7.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><br />\nPresent for the best questioner</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-8.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-9.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-10.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Gave the Placard to Mr. Rusmanto Maryanto ( Chairman Harian Asosiasi Open Source Indonesia )</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-11.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-12.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Gave the Placard to Mr. Khulung Bursa (Instruktur Oracle)</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-13.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-14.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Gave the Placard to Mrs. Yuliazmi M.Kom</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-15.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><br />\nEvaluation after the Seminar</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-16.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-17.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-18.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Shooting after the Seminar was a Joint Committee of Software Freedom Day, Speakers and<br />\nmoderators</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-19.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-20.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Games</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-21.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-22.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-23.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Workshop</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-24.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-25.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-26.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-27.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><br />\nWe as the committee of Software Freedom Day 2013 thanks to Rusmanto Maryanto (InfoLinux), Khulung Bursa (Oracle) as speaker, and Mrs. Yuliazmi M.Kom as Moderator, and of course all the participants Software Freedom Day 2013.</div>\n\n<p><iframe frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/lghgPmRHd0I\" width=\"560\"></iframe></p>\n', 'Software Freedom Day 2013 @ Universitas Budi Luhur ', '<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-1.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>On September 28, 2013</strong> Kelompok Studi Linux of the Budi Luhur University also participated in Software Freedom Day held an event 2013, the first event was a Seminar with the theme of the discussion regarding the safeguarding of Data Base System which was given the theme of &quot;Optimalisasi dan Pengamanan Database&quot;.&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">The event featured two speakers, the speaker first by Rusmanto Maryanto, who served as Chairman of the Association&#39;s member Indonesia Open Source material on the development of Free Open Source Software in Indonesia and the second by Bursa Khulung Speaker who served as an Oracle Instructor discusses about how to create a database that is secure from different sides of the application.</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">In addition to the Seminars and events Workshop held on 27 September 2013 ladder which discusses how the installation of linux and how to create a web server and for entertainment there is the show match game with the name of the game in the arena of open play in the linux operating system.</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Before we held the seminar</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Presentation By Rusmanto Maryanto ( Chairman Harian Asosiasi Open Source Indonesia )</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-2.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-3.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Presentation By Khulung Bursa (Oracle Instructu