1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-20.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Games</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-21.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-22.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-23.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Workshop</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-24.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-25.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-26.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2013-universitas-27.jpg\" style=\"height:480px; width:640px\" /></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><br />\nWe as the committee of Software Freedom Day 2013 thanks to Rusmanto Maryanto (InfoLinux), Khulung Bursa (Oracle) as speaker, and Mrs. Yuliazmi M.Kom as Moderator, and of course all the participants Software Freedom Day 2013.</div>\n\n<p><iframe frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/lghgPmRHd0I\" width=\"560\"></iframe></p>\n', 0, 0, '2018-09-08 10:55:11', '2018-09-08 10:55:11', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, 1, 1);
