(7, 'Software Freedom Day 2014 ', '<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/header_page-bg2.png\" style=\"height:191px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Software Freedom Day (SFD)</strong> adalah perayaan tahunan di seluruh dunia dari Free Software. SFD merupakan upaya pendidikan publik dengan tujuan meningkatkan kesadaran Free Software dan kebajikan, dan mendorong penggunaannya.</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Software Freedom Day didirikan pada tahun 2004 dan pertama kali diamati pada 28 Agustus tahun itu. Sekitar 12 tim berpartisipasi dalam Software Freedom Day pertama. Sejak saat itu telah berkembang dalam popularitas dan sementara penyelenggara diantisipasi lebih dari 1.000 tim pada tahun 2010.</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Sejak tahun 2006 Software Freedom Day telah diselenggarakan pada hari Sabtu ketiga bulan September, kadang-kadang bertepatan dengan <em>&nbsp;International Talk Like a Pirate Day</em>.</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Di Indonesia sendiri tidak banyak kelompok-kelompok tertentu atau institusi pemerintah/non-pemerintah yang ikut merayakan Software Freedom Day. Pantauan dari kami sendiri di Event Maps Software Freedom Day dari tahun ke tahun, hanya tahun 2009 lebih dari 10 team dari Indonesia ikut merayakan dan berpatisipasi dalam Software Freedom Day.</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Diantara team-team tersebut, salah satunya adalah kami, yaitu <strong>Kelompok Studi Linux &ndash; Universitas Budi Luhur</strong>, kami sendiri sudah ikut merayakan dan berpartisipasi dalam acara tahunan Software Freedom Day sejak tahun 2010 (Terdaftar -red).</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Untuk tahun 2014 ini pada tanggal 20 September nanti, KSL-UBL merayakan Software Freedom Day dengan membuat acara Seminar dengan tema &ldquo;Big Data Cloud Computing&rdquo; dan tidak lupa memberi pencerahan terhadap peserta yang hadir dengan menjelaskan apa itu <strong>FOSS</strong> (<em>Free Open Source Software</em>). Dalam event tahunan kali ini KSL-UBL mengundang 2 orang pembicara yang ahli dalam bidangnya yaitu <strong>Bapak</strong> <strong>Rusmanto Maryanto</strong> (Ketua Yayasan Penggerak Linux Indonesia) yang berkompeten dalam bidang <em>Open Source</em> dan <strong>Bapak</strong> <strong>Heru Sutadi</strong> (Direktur Indonesia ICT Institue) yang berkompeten dalam bidang <em>Big Data&nbsp;Cloud Computing</em>. Serta kami dari KSL-UBL akan membuka booth/stand yang berkaitan dengan FOSS. Tidak hanya itu, kami juga akan memberikan Doorprize, Sertifikat dan masih banyak lagi!!! yang tentunya bakal membuat kalian merasa <strong>rugi</strong>&nbsp;jika tidak datang pada event Software Freedom Day yang kami adakan tahun ini.</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Tentunya event tahun 2014 ini sangat menarik bukan? Apa lagi ditengah-tengah trend nya teknologi <em>Cloud Computing</em> di Dunia dan masih jarangnya perusahaan atau instansi lain di Indonesia yang belum menggunakan teknologi Cloud ini.</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2014-flyer.jpg\" style=\"height:640px; width:452px\" /></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Buat kalian yang berkeinginan untuk berpatisipasi merayakan <strong>Software Freedom Day 2014&nbsp;</strong>yang kami adakan, silakan&nbsp;daftarkan diri kalian&nbsp;ke Contact Person ini 08979166154 (Iqbal) dan 08999193317 (Reza), atau kalian bisa mendaftar langsung di stand yang kami sediakan mulai tanggal 8 september 2014 di unit 6 lantai 1 (depan lift) Universitas Budi Luhur.</div>\n&nbsp;\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Acara tersebut akan dilaksanakan pada :</div>\n&nbsp;\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Hari, Tanggal &nbsp; : Sabtu,&nbsp;20 September 2014<br />\nPukul &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;:&nbsp;09.00 WIB - Selesai<br />\nTempat &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; :&nbsp;Ruang Theater (Unit 6 lt. 4) Universitas Budi Luhur</div>\n&nbsp;\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;<em>[FREE REGISTRATION]</em></div>\n&nbsp;\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><a href=\"http://goo.gl/yjILRk\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Events Map SFD 2014\"><strong>Events Map 2014</strong></a> (Update, September 07)</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/sfd2014.jpg\" style=\"height:414px; width:640px\" /></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">info lebih lanjut silahkan hubungi di Twitter kami <u><a href=\"https://twitter.com/kslubl\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"@kslubl\"><u>@<strong>kslubl</strong></u></a></u>.</div>\n&nbsp;\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>See You!!!</strong></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n', 'Software Freedom Day 2014 ', '<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/header_page-bg2.png\" style=\"height:191px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Software&nbsp;Freedom Day (SFD) is an annual worldwide celebration of Free Software. SFD is a community education effort with the aim of increasing Free Software awareness and virtue, and encouraging its use.<br />\n<br />\nFreedom Day software was founded in 2004 and the first time on August 28 of that year. About 12 times in the first Freedom Day Software. Currently it has grown in popularity and while organizers anticipated more than 1,000 teams in 2010.<br />\n<br />\nIn 2006 Freedom Day Software was held on Saturday September, sometimes coinciding with International Talk Like a Pirate Day.<br />\n<br />\nIn Indonesia, there are not many specific groups or those who participate in Freedom Day Software. Monitoring from our own on the Freedom Day Event Maps Software from year to year, only in 2009 more than 10 teams from Indonesia celebrated and participated in Freedom Day Software.<br />\n<br />\nAmong these teams, one of them is us, namely the Linux Study Group - Budi Luhur University, we ourselves have participated in the Freedom Day Software program since 2010 (Registered-ed).<br />\n<br />\nFor 2014 on September 20th, KSL-UBL celebrated Freedom Day Software by creating a Seminar with the theme &quot;Big Data Cloud Computing&quot; and did not forget to give enlightenment to participants who attended by explaining what FOSS (Free Open Source Software) was. In this event, this time KSL-UBL invited 2 speakers who were experts in their fields, namely Mr. Rusmanto Maryanto (Chair of the Indonesian Linux Driving Foundation) who was competent in the field of Open Source and Mr. Heru Sutadi (Director of Indonesia ICT Institute) who was competent in the field of Big Data Cloud Computing. As well as us from KSL-UBL will open a booth / stand discussing with FOSS. Not only that, we will also give Doorprizes, Certificates and much more !!! those who want to bring make you feel honored not to come on the Freedom Day Software program that we held this year.<br />\n<br />\nSurely this 2014 event is very interesting isn&#39;t it? What&#39;s more in the midst of the trend of Cloud Computing technology in the World and the scarcity of companies or others in Indonesia that have not used this Cloud technology.</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-2014-flyer.jpg\" style=\"height:640px; width:452px\" /></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">For those of you who wish to participate in celebrating our 2014 Freedom Day Software, please register yourself with this Contact Person 08979166154 (Iqbal) and 08999193317 (Reza), or you can register directly at the stand that we provide starting on September 8, 2014 in the unit 6 1st floor (in front of the lift) Budi Luhur University.<br />\n<br />\nThe event will be held on:<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nDay, Date: Saturday, September 20, 2014<br />\nAt 09.00 WIB - Finish<br />\nPlace: Theater Room (Unit 6 lt. 4) Budi Luhur University</div>\n&nbsp;\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;<em>[FREE REGISTRATION]</em></div>\n&nbsp;\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><a href=\"http://goo.gl/yjILRk\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Events Map SFD 2014\"><strong>Events Map 2014</strong></a> (Update, September 07)</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/sfd2014.jpg\" style=\"height:414px; width:640px\" /></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">more info please contact us on Twitter @kslubl.</div>\n&nbsp;\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>See You!!!</strong></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n', 0, 0, '2018-09-08 11:16:17', '2018-09-08 11:16:17', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, 1, 1),
(8, 'Perayaan Software Freedom Day 2014 ', '<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-1.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><strong>Happy SFD!</strong> - Pada tanggal 20 September 2014, <strong>Kelompok Studi Linux &ndash; Universitas Budi Luhur</strong> (<strong>KSL-UBL</strong>) kembali mengadakan event internasional tahunan setiap bulan September yaitu <strong><em>Software Freedom Day</em></strong>. Acara yang bertempat di Ruang Teater - Universitas Budi Luhur ini merupakan salah satu perayaan dan gerakan untuk mendukung Kebebasan dalam menggunakan Software atau <strong>Free Open Source Software</strong> diseluruh dunia.</p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-2.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-3.jpg\" style=\"height:356px; width:640px\" /></div>\n\n<p>Pada tahun ini <strong>KSL-UBL</strong> bersama <strong>Jalantikus.com</strong> sebagai Sponsor Utama, mengadakan Seminar dengan mengambil tema &ldquo;<em>Big Data Cloud Computing</em>&rdquo;. Acara seminar ini diisi oleh Narasumber yang ahli dalam bidangnya, <strong>Bapak Rusmanto Maryanto</strong> dan <strong>Bapak</strong> <strong>Heru Sutadi</strong>. Tidak hanya itu acara ini juga di moderatori oleh <strong>Ibu Yuliazmi, M.Kom</strong> selaku Dosen Universitas Budi Luhur.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-4.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">Dalam pemaparan yang disampaikan oleh <strong>Bapak Rusmanto</strong>, beliau menyampaikan bahwa Pentingnya Penguasaan Open Source di Era Big Data dan Cloud Computing.</div>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-5.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p>Tidak hanya itu, dalam pemaparan yang disampaikan <strong>Bapak Heru Sutadi</strong>, beliau menyampaikan Infrastruktur menjadi tantangan utama Big Data diikuti soal privasi dan keamanan, kualitas dan tak ketinggalan adalah Edukasi.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-6.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Karena keterbatasannya waktu, dalam sesi tanya jawab banyak peserta yang belum puas dalam pemaparan yang disampaikan oleh kedua narasumber tersebut, terlihat dari banyaknya antusias peserta yang ingin bertanya lebih jauh tentang Open Source di Era Cloud Computing itu sendiri.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-7.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p>Selain itu event ini juga dimeriahkan dengan acara pembagian Buku, Doorprize, Goody bag, dan t-shirt dari pihak <strong>KSL-UBL</strong> bersama <strong>Jalantikus.com</strong>, bagi peserta yang beruntung mendapatkannya.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-8.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-9.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Selesai pembagian hadiah, kami selaku pihak <strong>KSL-UBL</strong> memberikan Piagam kepada <strong>Bapak Rusmanto Maryanto</strong> dan <strong>Bapak Heru Sutadi</strong> sebagai Narasumber, <strong>Ibu Yuliazmi, M.kom</strong> sebagai Moderator, dan juga <strong>Jalantikus.com</strong> sebagai Sponsor utama di <strong>Software Freedom Day 2014</strong>.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-10.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-11.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-12.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-13.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Kami <strong>Kelompok Studi Linux &ndash; Universitas Budi Luhur</strong> berbangga, karena merupakan salah satu dari sekian banyak organisasi/kelompok studi/komunitas di seluruh dunia terutama Indonesia yang ikut berpartisipasi dalam kegiatan <strong>Software Freedom Day 2014</strong>.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-14.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-15.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Kelompok Studi Linux &ndash; Universitas Budi Luhur</strong> (<strong>KSL-UBL</strong>) mengucapkan terima kasih kepada pihak Kampus UBL, Narasumber, Moderator, Sponsor (<strong>JalanTikus.com</strong>), Peserta, serta pihak-pihak yang turut memeriahkan dan mensukseskan event tahunan ini.</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">See you next year in <em><strong>Software Freedom Day 2015!</strong></em></div>\n', 'Celebration of 2014 Freedom Day Software', '<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-1.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><strong>Happy SFD!</strong> - On September 20, 2014, the <strong>Linux Study Group - Budi Luhur University (KSL-UBL)</strong> again held an annual international event every September, namely <em><strong>Software Freedom Day</strong></em>. The event which took place in the Budi Luhur University Theater Room is one of the celebrations and movements to support Freedom in using Software or <strong>Free Open Source Software</strong> throughout the world.</p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-2.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-3.jpg\" style=\"height:356px; width:640px\" /></div>\n\n<p>This year the <strong>KSL-UBL</strong> with<strong> Jalantikus.com</strong> as the Main Sponsor, held a Seminar taking the theme &quot;<em>Big Data Cloud Computing</em>&quot;. The seminar was filled by resource persons who were experts in their fields, <strong>Mr. Rusmanto Maryanto</strong> and <strong>Mr. Heru Sutadi</strong>. Not only that, this event was also moderated by Ms. Yuliazmi, M.Kom as a Lecturer at Budi Luhur University.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-4.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">In the presentation delivered by <strong>Mr. Rusmanto</strong>, he said that the Importance of Open Source is Mastered in the Big Data and Cloud Computing Era.</div>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-5.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Not only that, in the presentation delivered by <strong>Mr. Heru Sutadi</strong>, he said that Infrastructure is the main challenge for Big Data, followed by privacy and security, quality and education.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-6.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Due to time constraints, in the question and answer session many participants were not satisfied in the presentation delivered by the two speakers, as seen from the many enthusiastic participants who wanted to ask further about Open Source in the Cloud Computing Era itself.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-7.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p>In addition, this event was also enlivened with the distribution of books, door prizes, goody bags and t-shirts from <strong>KSL-UBL</strong> with <strong>Jalantikus.com</strong>, for those who were lucky to get them.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-8.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-9.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Selesai pembagian hadiah, kami selaku pihak <strong>KSL-UBL</strong> memberikan Piagam kepada <strong>Bapak Rusmanto Maryanto</strong> dan <strong>Bapak Heru Sutadi</strong> sebagai Narasumber, <strong>Ibu Yuliazmi, M.kom</strong> sebagai Moderator, dan juga <strong>Jalantikus.com</strong> sebagai Sponsor utama di <strong>Software Freedom Day 2014</strong>.</p>\n\n<p>After the prize distribution, we as the <strong>KSL-UBL</strong> gave Charter to <strong>Mr. Rusmanto Maryanto</strong> and <strong>Mr. Heru Sutadi</strong> as Resource persons, <strong>Ms. Yuliazmi, M.kom</strong> as Moderators, and also <strong>Jalantikus.com</strong> as the main Sponsor in <strong>Software Freedom Day 2014 </strong>.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-10.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-11.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-12.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-13.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>We are <strong>the Linux Study Group - Budi Luhur University</strong> is proud, because it is one of the many organizations / study groups / communities throughout the world, especially Indonesia, which participated in the <strong>Software Freedom Day 2014</strong> activities.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-14.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/perayaan-software-freedom-day-2014-15.jpg\" style=\"height:390px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Kelompok Studi Linux &ndash; Universitas Budi Luhur</strong> (<strong>KSL-UBL</strong>) would like to thank the Campus UBL, Resources, Moderators, Sponsors (<strong>JalanTikus.com</strong>), Participants, as well as those who helped enliven and succeed this annual event.</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:justify\">See you next year in <em><strong>Software Freedom Day 2015!</strong></em></div>\n', 0, 0, '2018-09-08 11:41:01', '2018-09-08 11:41:01', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, 1, 1),
(9, 'Workshop Introduction Web Server With Drupal 7 On FreeBSD ', '<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/workshop-introduction-web-server-with-1.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:&quot;verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><strong>Happy SFD! -</strong> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">Pada Tanggal 18 September 2015, <span style=\"font-family:&quot;verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">dalam men<span style=\"font-family:&quot;verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">yambut <span style=\"font-family:&quot;verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">event Software Freedom Day <span style=\"font-family:&quot;verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">tahun 2015, K<span style=\"font-family:&quot;verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">elompok Studi Linux - Universitas B<span style=\"font-family:&quot;verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">u<span style=\"font-family:&quot;verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">di Luhur mengadakan be<span style=\"font-family:&quot;verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">rbagai rangkaian acara</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>, salah satunya Workshop.&nbsp;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">Pada<span style=\"font-family:&quot;verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"> a</span>cara workshop Software Freedom Day yang bertemakan <strong><em>Introduction Web Server With Drupal 7 On FreeBSD</em></strong> yang dibawakan oleh Om Andy Hidayat selaku pembicara. </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">Sepertinya Peserta cukup antusias, </span></span>terlihat dari bagaimana peserta mendengarkan penjelasan dari Om Andy Hidayat.</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/workshop-introduction-web-server-with-2.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/workshop-introduction-web-server-with-3.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:&quot;verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">Banyak peserta yang belum mengetahui tentang Drupal 7<strong> </strong>yang dikenal sebagai CMS.<strong> </strong>Dengan adanya workshop ini peserta menjadi tau tentang kegunaan web server di sistem operasi FreeBSD dan tidak hanya sampai disitu saja, FreeBSD mengajarkan tentang freedom, dan sharing kepada semua orang.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/workshop-introduction-web-server-with-4.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/workshop-introduction-web-server-with-5.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p>Dengan adanya event seperti Software Freedom Day ini, mendorong rasa keingintahuan peserta akan software open source, dan meningkatkan minat peserta untuk menggunakan software open source.</p>\n\n<p>(Sesi Foto Bersama Workshop Introduction Web Server With Drupal 7 On FreeBSD)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/workshop-introduction-web-server-with-6.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/workshop-introduction-web-server-with-7.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /></p>\n', 'Workshop Introduction Web Server With Drupal 7 On FreeBSD ', '<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/workshop-introduction-web-server-with-1.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><strong>Happy SFD!</strong> - On September 18, 2015, in welcoming the 2015 Software Freedom Day event, the Linux Study Group - Budi Luhur University held various events, one of which was Workshop.<br />\n<br />\nAt the Freedom Day Software workshop, the theme was <em><strong>Introduction to Web Server With Drupal 7 On FreeBSD</strong></em> hosted by Om Andy Hidayat as the speaker. It looks like the participants are quite enthusiastic, seen from how the participants listened to the explanation from Om Andy Hidayat.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/workshop-introduction-web-server-with-2.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/workshop-introduction-web-server-with-3.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p>Many participants who do not know about Drupal 7 are known as CMS. With this workshop, participants learned about the use of web servers in the FreeBSD operating system and not only there, FreeBSD taught about freedom, and shared with everyone.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/workshop-introduction-web-server-with-4.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/workshop-introduction-web-server-with-5.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p>With this event such as Freedom Day Software, encouraging participants &#39;curiosity about open source software, and increasing participants&#39; interest in using open source software.<br />\n<br />\n(Workshop Photo Sharing Session Introduction to Web Servers With Drupal 7 On FreeBSD)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/workshop-introduction-web-server-with-6.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/workshop-introduction-web-server-with-7.jpg\" style=\"height:360px; width:640px\" /></p>\n', 0, 0, '2018-09-08 11:50:41', '2018-09-08 11:50:41', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, 1, 1),
(10, 'Software Freedom Day KSL Budi Luhur 2017 ', '<p>Perayaan Perangkat lunak bebas dan open source yang diadakan setiap tahunnya setiap bulan September. Agenda tahunan yang diadakan KSL Budi Luhur sendiri, acara tersebut terdiri dari Workshop dan Talk Show.</p>\n\n<p>Software Freedom Day(SFD) tahun ini bertema Keep Our System Safe yang diadakan pada tanggal 16 dan 18 September 2017 yang dilaksanakan di Fakultas Teknologi Informasi Universitas Budi Luhur.</p>\n\n<p>Dimulai hari Sabtu 16 September 2017, dilaksanakan workshop Peningkatan keamanan Attack dan Defense with OWASP oleh Ade Yoseman Putra(OWASP Indonesia Chapter).</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-ksl-budi-luhur-2017-1.jpg\" style=\"height:453px; width:606px\" /></p>\n\n<p>Hari Senin&nbsp; 18 September 2017, dilaksanakan Talk Show yang berjudul Super Heroes of Company oleh Dr. Tjahjanto, S.Kom(Founder, CEO, IT consultant), Prighadi, S.T(Senior Computer Networking).</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-ksl-budi-luhur-2017-2.jpg\" style=\"height:427px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p>KSL Budi Luhur juga mengadakan lomba selfie dan penyerahan hadiah pada selfie terbaik.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-ksl-budi-luhur-2017-3.jpg\" style=\"height:426px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p>itulah keseruan SFD tahun ini, tunggu keseruan SFD di tahun Berikutnya.</p>\n', 'Software Freedom Day KSL Budi Luhur 2017 ', '<p>Celebration Free and open source software that is held annually every September. The annual agenda held by KSL Budi Luhur itself, the event consisted of Workshop and Talk Show.<br />\n<br />\nThis year&#39;s Software Freedom Day (SFD) with the theme of Keep Our System Safe held on September 16 and 18, 2017 was held at the Budi Luhur University Information Technology Faculty.<br />\n<br />\nStarting on Saturday 16 September 2017, a workshop was held to increase the security of Attack and Defense with OWASP by Ade Yoseman Putra (OWASP Indonesia Chapter).</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-ksl-budi-luhur-2017-1.jpg\" style=\"height:453px; width:606px\" /></p>\n\n<p>Monday, September 18, 2017, a Talk Show entitled Super Heroes of Company was held by Dr. Tjahjanto, S.Kom (Founder, CEO, IT consultant), Prighadi, S.T (Senior Computer Networking).</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-ksl-budi-luhur-2017-2.jpg\" style=\"height:427px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p>KSL Budi Luhur also holds a selfie competition and presents prizes at the best selfies.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/images/software-freedom-day-ksl-budi-luhur-2017-3.jpg\" style=\"height:426px; width:640px\" /></p>\n\n<p>that&#39;s the excitement of SFD this year, wait for the excitement of SFD in the following year.</p>\n', 0, 0, '2018-09-08 11:57:16', '2018-09-08 11:57:16', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, 1, 1);

